svg.text: PostgreSQL Diesel Models & Schemas for Rust

div.p: pg_diesel provides comprehensive Diesel ORM schemas and models for PostgreSQL system catalogs, enabling type-safe database introspection and metaprogramming. The library exposes 216 tables and views from information_schema, pg_catalog, and PostGIS, supporting code generation, schema analysis, and runtime database reflection. Extensively tested via CI across all supported PostgreSQL versions with full code coverage reporting.

svg.text: Complete Diesel table definitions for PostgreSQL system catalogs
Feature flags handle version-specific columns and system catalog differences
Core capabilities for database introspection and code generation
